data.description: Here's your opportunity! Buyer's financing fell through so this stunning home is back on the market, and it's your fortunate moment to become the proud owner of this beautiful home! This exceptional custom-built Limestone home was designed as a one-and-a-half-story gem! Step onto the inviting covered porch before entering the open great room with its soaring cathedral ceilings and custom fireplace. The spacious kitchen boasts beautifully crafted Amish cabinets, a bay window, separate coffee bar and pantry closet. Beautiful French doors lead out to a delightful 2-tiered deck, perfect for outdoor gatherings.  The first floor features two bedrooms and a full bath, conveniently accompanied by a laundry room and an additional half bath. Ascend to the second floor to discover a generously sized third bedroom, a full bath, and a large loft that could serve as an ideal home office space or a 4th bedroom.  Outside, imagine the tranquility of your own private oasis in this property's fully fenced yard. The convenience of a shed with electrical power supply opens up endless possibilities, whether for storage, hobbies, or creative endeavors. The lighted arbor with a swing adds a touch of charm, creating an inviting space for relaxing evenings or entertaining guests. The property also includes a 2.5 car garage with a workshop/gym and an exterior service door leading to the backyard. Noteworthy updates include a 2017 water heater, a deck installed in 2017, and a gas furnace replaced in 2016, new roof 2020 and garage landing remodel 2020. The home is well-insulated with Anderson thermal pane windows and offers both gas and electric hook-ups for the dryer or stove. Located in the esteemed Limestone school district, this home is a true gem. Schedule your private showing today.
